Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.93,0:00:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined his arms could still move \Non their own after being detached!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.92,0:00:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when did he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.17,0:00:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I threw the explosive tags?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hid in the smoke long enough to send his right arm underground!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a true blue Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their abilities are all out of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said we were finished, but you still had no idea what I was capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was better to keep your distance as you played your next hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.01,0:00:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually think, unlike my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Kakuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something, Kakuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:00:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Chouji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nikudan Hari Sensha{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:04.70,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}(Nikudan Hari Sensha: Spiked Meat Tank)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.26,0:01:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My god...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like Naruto's taken a single break.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.35,0:01:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't think so. He has to perfect his new technique as soon as possible, if we're going to be sent as Kakashi-sensei's backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time limit's twenty-four hours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a difficult situation, but all we can do is believe in Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:02:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're the only team who can \Nwork smoothly with Kakashi-sensei's.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've almost got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I finish, I'll catch up to Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:03:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you need to be wary of Sasuke's fire element.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time I explained the elemental vulnerabilities \Nof the five nature manipulation types.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're elemental vulnerabilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To put it simply, fire, water, wind, lightning and earth each have an elemental advantage and vulnerability connecting them to the other elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me draw you a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are five types of nature manipulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they are, drawn in a circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's take fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll add its relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's stronger than wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:05:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but at the same time, it's weak against water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each element has an advantage over another and is weak to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't get a word I'm saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dumbing it down even further,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto, your wind element techniques will lose \Nagainst Sasuke's fire element ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to beat fire is water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't wind beat fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When fire comes into contact with wind, it burns stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you throw water on it, it goes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:06:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, if you countered Sasuke's fire techniques with a wind one of the same strength, it'd backfire by making the fire even larger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But take a look at wind's relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wind is weak against fire, but strong against lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that your new technique can overcome Sasuke's ultimate lightning technique Chidori!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto, it's a good thing you didn't have an earth affinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I have the correct affinity for Sasuke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Wind is the one element that can defeat lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that can save a fire from dying, and give it even more power, is wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:06:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your training is progressing well, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.29,0:07:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be finished soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us a little more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just like Raidou-senpai described!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotta be a body-solidifying technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's his ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another good analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. No physical attack can harm me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accounted for their abilities up to a point, but this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If direct attacks won't work, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cower in fear, you pathetic atheists!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, now it's our turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakuzu, break this technique already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How the hell...? I couldn't even sense you, and you got me from behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cower in fear, you pathetic atheists!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, now it's our turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakuzu, break this technique already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How the hell...? I couldn't even sense you, and you got me from behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought physical attacks didn't work on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Kakashi-sensei, how did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw everything. I watched you perform that iron-skin technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The seals you used were for earth-typed nature manipulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It only took me a second. You managed to read my seals at that speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to use such a powerful lightning technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I get it! You're Sharingan Kakashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earth is weak against lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.31,0:10:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got matched with the wrong guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi-sensei really is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we've just got one left to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was so quick! Kakashi-sensei really is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Things would be a lot tougher if we \Ndidn't take out the mortal one first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.61,0:10:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Shikamaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Shadow Mimic's reaching its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he get your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just go around getting killed outta nowhere. Man, you suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're next.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he gets for acting cool and saying crap like, "You're dead."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I missed his heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice. Now let's slaughter these idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold the Shadow Mimic any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Shikamaru, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why didn't that guy die after getting hit by Raikiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with these two, nothing they do surprises me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, I can move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:13:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you ready to kill them, Kakuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.99,0:13:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chakra they're giving off is disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Jashin, watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go nuts, seriously, go crazy, non-stop insane on all of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready, Chouji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.53,0:14:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakuzu! Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of 'em died right after you let it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, could you suck any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.88,0:15:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If one of those masks died right after it was released,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then it must've been what I hit with Raikiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hidan, sit this one out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I'm getting really pissed that they keep tricking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it like always, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fuuton, Atsugai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:11.05,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}(Fuuton, Atsugai: Wind Element, Bleeding Force)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chouji, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... He even attacked his partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! They're taking advantage of his immortality!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes, Chouji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they can't let that hit them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chouji, Shikamaru, get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Raiton, Gian{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:50.95,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}(Raiton, Gian: Lightning Element, Mock Darkness)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.49,0:18:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys are strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the one in the mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.99,0:19:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one should be able to use elemental attacks at this level unless they had the innate affinity for the element.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's already used earth, wind, and now lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first person to survive that combo, Hatake Kakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Sharingan saved him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But can he keep it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Katon, Zukokku{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:48.00,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}(Katon, Zukokku: Fire Element, Cranium Carver)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be easier to fight them if we could just split them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means we need someone to take care of Hidan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll use my Mind-Body Switch technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.82,0:21:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you go, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.06,0:21:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he even scratches you with an attack and gets your blood, you're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But-!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle him all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.11,0:21:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And fulfill {\i1}that{\i0} role as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Terrifying Secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sai-kun, what are you doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.56,0:22:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just drawing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.48,0:22:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? You're not very energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.75,0:22:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look pale!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.78,0:22:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A burning vigor is what makes the youth young! And you're lacking passion!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm going to give you a very special item as a present!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.71,0:22:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.54,0:22:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.95,0:22:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This gorgeous suit is specially made so it breathes, \Nis durable, and always fits perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.96,0:22:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the perfect bodysuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.90,0:22:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I wear one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a highly sought-after item and is hard to get your hands on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.33,0:22:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at these beautiful body lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee that if you wear it during training once, \Nyou'll never be able to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is truly a miracle gown for all youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.02,0:22:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A miracle gown?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.39,0:22:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just between the two of us, this suit has made \Nboth Naruto and Lee power up big time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.23,0:22:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:22:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what happened. So how does it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.07,0:23:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be blunt, gay.
